data.description: You won't want to miss this beautiful  Torresdale brick front twin. Enter into a spacious living room with refinished hard ward floors, recessed lighting and large window that fills the room with natural light. Next you will find the dining area and beautiful kitchen with granite countertops with subway tiled backsplash, breakfast bar and newer stainless steel appliances. Finishing off the main level is a powder room. Onto the upper level welcomes you with a large master bedroom, with his and her closets. Also on the second floor you will find 2 additional bedrooms and an updated full bath with soaking tub and shower. The basement is fully finished and is a great space and has plenty of storage. Last but not least,  step out to a large rear yard that won't disappoint,  a covered patio highlights the space and will make for a great summer of entertaining.
